Software for the UNIX System is packaged in sets. Installation of the
Foundation Set is required.  This software is shipped to you either on a
second group of diskettes (different from the boot diskettes) or on a
cartridge tape.  

Select the drive you will be using to install the Foundation Set.
.optstring
Your choices are:
